Class PointsCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • BT.managers.PointsCalculator

  • public class PointsCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that will calculate star and end points for given object. This class will calculate start and end point by given objects, just pass 2 objects in it and it ethod will handle everzthing else. To get calculated points call for getStartPoint and getEndPoint

    Karel Hala
